{"type":"miscellaneous","title":"Shiverthorn","summaries":["<b>Shiverthorn</b> is a type of herb that grows naturally on snow and ice blocks of any type. It can be harvested with any weapon or tool, and can be planted manually with Shiverthorn Seeds, which can also be planted in Clay Pots and Planter Boxes.","Shiverthorn will always bloom after a period of growth, and unlike other herbs, remain bloomed permanently thereafter. Fully grown Shiverthorn emits a glowing particle effect. Harvesting Shiverthorn while in bloom yields 1-3 Shiverthorn Seeds in addition to the Shiverthorn item.","<span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> Both Shiverthorn and their respective seeds have a chance to be obtained from the Herb Bag."],"statistics":{"Max stack":"999 <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 99 <span class=\"eico s i3 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span>","Rarity":"<span class=\"rarity\">[img:Rarity level: 0]</span>","Sell":"<span class=\"coin\" title=\"20 Copper Coins\" data-sort-value=\"20\"><span class=\"cc\">20</span></span>","Research":"<abbr class=\"journey\" title=\"Journey Mode\">25 required</abbr>"},"crafts":{"Used in":[{"result":{"rowspan":1,"value":"<span class=\"i multi-line\">[img:Garland]<span><span>Garland</span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span></span>"},"ingredients":{"value":"<ul><li><span class=\"i\">[img:Daybloom]<span><span>Daybloom</span></span></span></li><li><span class=\"i\">[img:Moonglow]<span><span>Moonglow</span></span></span></li><li><span class=\"i\">[img:Blinkroot]<span><span>Blinkroot</span></span></span></li><li><span class=\"i\">[img:Waterleaf]<span><span>Waterleaf</span></span></span></li><li><span class=\"i\">[img:Deathweed]<span><span>Deathweed</span></span></span></li><li><s